      <p style=\"font-family:Space Grotesk;font-size:12px;color:#CBCDD8;margin:0;line-height:1.45;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-break:break-word;\">The felt sense, internal parts narrative, and meaning made of the experience.</p>\n            </div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-radius:10px;padding:24px 20px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;\">\ud83e\uddec</div>\n                <h3 style=\"font-family:Space Grotesk;font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:#ECEEF5;margin:0 0 6px;line-height:1.2;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-break:break-word;\">Objective (UR)</h3>\n                <p style=\"font-family:Space Grotesk;font-size:12px;color:#CBCDD8;margin:0;line-height:1.45;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-break:break-word;\">Nervous system dysregulation, hypervigilance, and somatic freeze responses.</p>\n            </div></div></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
